			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I have Azdalin's and Gylton's scale, working on getting Xyfl's scale, which does indeed seem to be the rare one (found many people with A and G scales).  I'll post here when I complete the quest if nobody else does first.<BR>
<BR>
For the record, the scales are called wurm scales and do not say the name unless identified.  They are LORE and look completely identical, which can make it hard to tell which one you have as a warrior.  Be wary of getting the wrong scale, either by mistake or scam.
