			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The award for this quest is this:<BR>
<BR>
Wurmslayer<BR>
MAGIC ITEM<BR>
Skill: Piercing<BR>
Damage: 25<BR>
Delay: 40<BR>
AC: 5<BR>
STR: +5<BR>
SV MAGIC: +5<BR>
WT: 15.0<BR>
Range: 20<BR>
Class: WAR PAL RNG SHD<BR>
Race: ALL<BR>
<BR>
Couple of things to note:  Paladins don't get any piercing skill, so they can't use this as a weapon.  They can put this in their range slot though.  It also only fits in the primary hand of a warrior or ranger.  Also, notice that it's not lore, so you can be using one AND have one in your range slot.<BR>
<BR>
You have to turn 3 Dragon Scales in to Squire Fuzzmin.  The 3 scales identify as 'Azdalin', 'Gylton', and 'Xyfyl'.  Notice that when he gives you the quest, he says 'Xyfl'.  This is a misspelling.<BR>
<BR>
I'll leave it up to you to figure out where to get the 3 scales ;)<BR>
<BR>
-Andorion<BR>
 berjd@ucla.edu
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
